sql:
SELECT lens_name
FROM contact_lenses
WHERE lens_id = (SELECT lens_id FROM feedback WHERE feedback_id = 1);

SELECT AVG(f.rating) AS avg_rating
FROM feedback f
WHERE f.lens_id = 0;

SELECT inventory_id
FROM inventory
WHERE stock_quantity < reorder_level;

external_knowledge:
- "most popular" refers to the lenses with the highest average rating; 
- "recently" refers to within the last month;
- "average ratings" refers to the mean of ratings given by customers.

